  <brief_title>Intracorporeal Versus Extracorporeal Mechanical Anastomosis in Laparoscopic Right Colectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Intracorporeal Versus Extracorporeal Mechanical Anastomosis in Laparoscopic Right Colectomy. A Prospective Randomized Controlled Clinical Trial</official_title>
